body:
The following query returns the documents that match the search
criteria.

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "phrase": {
        "path": "title",
        "query": "new york"
      }
    }
  },
  { $limit: 10 },
  {
    $project: {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1,
      score: { $meta: "searchScore" }
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```shell
[
  { title: 'New York, New York', score: 6.786321640014648 }
  { title: 'New York', score: 6.258549213409424 }
